data.description: This end unit townhome is well maintained and it will be a great property for a first time home buyer or investor. It features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathroom, new carpet, tile throughout the first floor, lots of storage, fenced back patio, low HOA fees. This 1,314sqft home was built in 1995. It's close to parks, stores, restaurants, schools, and more. It's a MUST see property.
